Ubuntu 10.04:

Install packages: libgtk2.0-dev libcfitsio3-dev libxt-dev libftdi-dev libraw1394-dev
Install pvcam (in pvcam subdir)
Build and install rspiusb kernel module (in pvcam/rspiusb subdir)
modprobe rspiusb
Update system udev to allow puokonui to run without root priviledges (in udev subdir)
Download and install ds9 from http://hea-www.harvard.edu/RD/ds9/
Download xpa source from http://hea-www.harvard.edu/RD/xpa/, build and install
copy libxpa.a to puoko-nui source dir
make
